injury.description: Aug 29: Coach Sean McVay said Thursday that Nacua (knee) has been practicing "fully," and "he'll be ready to roll," Stu Jackson of the Rams' official site reports.
Aug 26: Jackson (shoulder) practiced Monday and is likely to be ready for the start of the regular season, Stu Jackson of the Rams' official site reports.
Aug 1: Head coach Sean McVay told reporters Thursday that Havenstein left practice due to a foot injury, Jourdan Rodrigue of The Athletic reports.
Aug 27: Higbee (knee) will be on the PUP list to start the regular season, making him ineligible for at least the first four games, Adam Schefter of ESPN reports.
Aug 9: Jackson has been sidelined for the Rams' last two practices due to a soft tissue injury, Stu Jackson of the Rams' official site reports.
